snippet.title: BBC Newsbeat
snippet.description:
Hi - we're the team who "do the news" on BBC Radio 1 & 1Xtra. 
But that's radio and this is video - so we'll be putting a monthly documentary here on a range of different things. 
Every now and then we'll upload a shorter watch - something we've done which we think is good!
Obviously we'd love you to subscribe, and if you really want to make us smile turn on notifications so you don't miss the fruits of our labours!
